See the DockerHub site for more info:  

    https://hub.docker.com/r/lachele/openconnect-ssh-iceweasel/


Normal use:

    git pull https://github.com/Lachele/openconnect-ssh-iceweasel
    docker pull lachele/openconnect-ssh-iceweasel

    Terminal 1%  bash start_vpn.bash your.vpn.url   # open the VPN
    Terminal 2%  bash connect_command.bash          # get a terminal
    Terminal 3%  bash iceweasel_connect.bash        # start firefox


Files:

    build-command.bash        # command used to build the image
    connect_command.bash      # after starting container, start terminal
    Dockerfile                # Dockerfile for image
    iceweasel_connect.bash    # after starting container, start iceweasel
    run_no_vpn.bash           # start the container without openconnect
    start_vpn.bash            # start the container with openconnect
